{"tid":2503070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭中基首想愛你歌詞好屈機","createTime":"2021-04-24T18:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:41:07.000Z","uid":249721,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e31281b576a6dc88909b400dc2ee6e6de6d7d9f","tid":2503070,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"想愛你 日子為何都給錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果 當天偶然曾提起我<br />\n難道我 這樣已經足夠快樂<br />\n如果 沉默真的太多因我怕又出錯<br />\n不想躲 但怎麽跟你講 可否接受我<br />\n<br />\n而每次見你身邊許多許多個<br />\n假設你是我 怎可能沒妒忌 沒痛楚<br />\n再記掛你多少光陰瞬間不覺已消磨<br />\n來日老掉時 仍是獨個麽<br />\n<br />\n想到你 夜深中突然心痛過<br />\n求憑着一首歌 你一生都記得我<br />\n想愛你 日子為何都給錯過<br />\n多少個秋和冬走過 才肯喜歡我<br />\n<br />\n如果 只感到無聊才找我<br />\n能共你 說着笑都感到快樂<br />\n如果 何日街中碰到都見我是一個<br />\n可清楚 日子的喜與悲 想跟你渡過<br />\n<br />\n想到你 夜深中突然心痛過<br />\n求憑着這首歌 你一生都記得我<br />\n想愛你 像此生未真的愛過<br />\n多少個秋和冬走過 才可清楚我<br />\n怎麽你竟然捨得我 常孤單一個"},{"pid":"b73cf42649a7b6cf22b1e3e0f44ae0eb8cb52fc1","tid":2503070,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"想愛你 像此生未真的愛過"},{"pid":"f42f1785a2264e560ee5cbc7538e38564d4c812a","tid":2503070,"uid":249721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T18:06:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lMQdBoS4-oM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlMQdBoS4-oM&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=8bb45ad0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lMQdBoS4-oM</a>"},{"pid":"dba5b85d139da0afeeaecc81bdec06241a5113e3","tid":2503070,"uid":305631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"毒撚到"},{"pid":"5186c9e960f347d69a15a00d7709404ca48ba11f","tid":2503070,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-24T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mo